py price action as markets awaited the US jobs report on Friday. A stellar jobs</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1251664775/image_1251664775.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742742-markets-weekly-outlook-central-bank-focus-us-inflation-looms", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 07:20:00"}, {"id": "4742735", "title": "Lightspeed: Brighter Now Than In 2021", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Customer feedback improve business to growth continuously. Japanese barista in apron standing in the cashier counter and give the customer bill with smile at the coffee shop. Customer looking at the bill and make payment\" data-id=\"1473939572\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpri